quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  16,61,Si DEUS punished people their transgressions He annihilated omnis creature terra. He respites them pro specific predetermined temporis Dodum their interim finis they non delay it 1 hora nor advance it
  16,62,They ascribe to DEUS quod they dislike themselves tunc utter lie their suus tongues they est righteous! Sine any doubt they incurred Hell they rebelled
  16,63,De DEUS nos sent (messengers) communities vos devil adorned their works their eyes Consequently he est nunc their dominus they incurred painful retribution
  16,64,Nos revealed hoc scripture vos point them quod they dispute provisus guidance mercy people qui believe
  16,65,DEUS sends CAELUM AQUA revive TERRA it ABIIT! Hoc est (sufficient) proof people hear